ch your mouth."],[1454,1541,"You're in no position to be"],[1541,1666,"giving orders, considering"],[1666,1716,"you just put"],[1716,1816,"Grandma in the hospital."],[2104,2216,"Go wait for me over there."],[2216,2312,"Ok? I'll be right there."],[2441,2491,"Witch!"],[2904,2991,"You said Grandma's"],[2991,3054,"in the hospital?"],[3104,3166,"Because of you."],[3179,3291,"She got all worked up at your"],[3291,3416,"perfect little wedding and"],[3416,3529,"collapsed when she got home."],[3579,3666,"What room is she in?"],[3691,3766,"Why do you care?"],[3804,3966,"You're not a Lane anymore."],[3979,4016,"You're just some"],[4016,4141,"stupid idiot's wife."],[4279,4329,"You can say"],[4329,4391,"whatever you want."],[4504,4566,"But I'm gonna go"],[4566,4641,"see Grandma, okay?"],[4641,4754,"I have to make sure she's okay."],[4804,4904,"Stop showing fake concern."],[4941,5041,"You don't actually give a shit."],[5241,5354,"I don't have time for this."],[5354,5404,"I'm gonna go find-"],[5816,5866,"No."]],"37":[[483,608,"Let's go."],[883,1008,"Daxon, can you go check on Charlie?"],[1058,1108,"I'm gonna help Ellie"],[1108,1183,"pick up these papers."],[1870,1970,"So this is the"],[1970,2045,"medical report."],[2108,2295,"McLean's made a whole team of"],[2295,2458,"doctors for a"],[2458,2570,"little numb skull."],[2633,2720,"Must be important."],[2733,2783,"No."],[2895,2937,"No!"],[3483,3650,"If I just pushed her"],[3670,3750,"right now,"],[3795,3883,"no one would"],[3883,4033,"ever question it."],[4058,4170,"And she just fell trying to"],[4170,4245,"grab the report."],[4320,4395,"Not my fault."],[4470,4537,"Why?"],[4570,4770,"Why do you get everything?"],[4820,4883,"Why is your life"],[4883,5020,"so damn perfect?"],[5070,5133,"Ellie Lane..."],[5170,5245,"it's time you finally got"],[5245,5345,"what you deserved."],[6908,6995,"What?"],[7033,7270,"I thought he was mentally disabled!"],[7333,7425,"Wait, so...."],[7495,7608,"You're not-"]],"38":[[20,95,"Wait, so..."],[533,608,"I'