 shy on me."],[1454,1541,"Ellie, I'm going to take care"],[1541,1616,"of you, I promise."],[1679,1766,"Every single day."],[1816,1879,"I'm going to give you the"],[1879,1991,"life that you've always deserved."],[2054,2154,"And you're happy and safe."],[2416,2466,"Mr. McLean."],[2554,2679,"There were no surveillance"],[2679,2779,"cameras in that hallway."],[2804,2929,"Nothing got recorded."],[2979,3079,"Wait, cameras?"],[3116,3229,"It's about what happened earlier."],[3254,3454,"Your sweet little sister"],[3454,3566,"tried to push you out the window"],[3566,3691,"when you reached for the report."],[3716,3829,"If I hadn't got there in time,"],[3829,3929,"she would have killed you."],[3979,4041,"I don't get it."],[4041,4091,"She's your sister."],[4116,4204,"Why would she try to hurt you?"],[4291,4429,"No, we were switched at birth."],[4479,4804,"Annie is the real Lane family heiress."],[4829,5054,"I just lived her life"],[5054,5179,"accidentally as the Lane"],[5179,5279,"family's daughter for the"],[5279,5404,"last 17 years."],[5541,5616,"She hates me."],[6016,6104,"Honestly, I"],[6179,6304,"can kind of see why."],[6304,6404,"Hey, it's not your fault."],[6441,6566,"It's your parents' mistake."],[6566,6633,"It's not yours."],[6704,6779,"They're the ones that"],[6779,6929,"mistaken their own child."],[7016,7141,"What I really don't get is..."],[7304,7354,"Why would she"],[7354,7441,"want to hurt Grandma?"],[7516,7554,"Wait."],[7691,7766,"Annie's the reason why your"],[7766,7841,"grandma's paralyzed?"],[7916,7954,"Yeah."],[8004,8104,"Find out everything you can"],[8104,8166,"about Annie Lane."],[8216,8254,"Now."],[9241,9320,"Mom?"]],"40":[[4,104,"Are you still in contact with"],[104,191,"those traffickers?"],[216,266,"What?"],[329,429,"Are you out of your mind?"],[491,654,"If we get caught, we're finished."],[679,841,"I'm gonna get rid of Ellie."],[991,1104,"Sell her off to some awful"],[1104,1266,"guy on the sticks."],[1316,1466,"Someone mean, abusive..."],[1529,1654,"pr